= zosc

== DESCRIPTION:

Open Sound Control router using DNS Service Discovery (aka Bonjour, MDNS)

== SYNOPSIS:

run with
$ruby zosc.rb

Routes all messages received on port 9090 via unicast to all other instances of the software on a network or software registered as a _osc._udp zeroconf service.

All messages received are sent out on localhost port 9091.

See the Max MSP 5 example patcher for a demo.

== REQUIREMENTS & INSTALL:

* Ruby 1.9.1 or JRuby
* gem install dnssd
* gem install ruby-osc
